------------------------------------------------------------------------------
								Bug#001
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
"Synchronization Broken"
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Steps to reproduce:
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Start the Eclipse instance
2. Create a text model file e.g. "state.rtsys"
3. Type in the model "aLabel" 
4. Initialize synccharts_diagram file
5. Check if the EMF model is correct. The following should be seen:
  Region
   |
    -- State
       |
        -- id:anonymous
        -- label:ALabel
 6. Now modify the label in the diagram, e.g. change it to "anotherLabel"
 7. Here is the dirty bug: Synchronization is broken, 
 the rtsys model file and the diagram are not aware of their changes anymore. 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Suspected Reasons or other remarks things:
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Saving of the diagram works fine though...Does this have sth to do with the 
ITransientService???  

